ang":"sk","value":"ovocie mierneho pásma"},{"lang":"ru","value":"плоды культур умеренного климата"},{"lang":"ar","value":"فواكه المناطق المعتدلة"},{"lang":"cs","value":"ovoce mírného pásma"},{"lang":"de","value":"Obst aus gemäßigten Breiten"},{"lang":"en","value":"temperate fruits"},{"lang":"fa","value":"میوه‌های معتدله"},{"lang":"fr","value":"fruits tempérés"},{"lang":"hi","value":"शीतोष्ण फल"},{"lang":"hu","value":"mérsékeltövi gyümölcs"},{"lang":"it","value":"Frutta delle zone temperate"},{"lang":"ja","value":"温帯果実"},{"lang":"ko","value":"온대과수"},{"lang":"lo","value":"ໝາກໄມ້ເຂດໜາວ"},{"lang":"pl","value":"Owoc klimatu umiarkowanego"},{"lang":"pt","value":"fruta de clima temperado"}]},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_0aa03a1e","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAOTERM","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-03-25T17:04:30"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"es","value":"El fruto es una drupa de tamaños diversos, según las variedades, de forma ovoide y color amarillo anaranjado,tanto la piel como la pulpa. Tiene una piel muy delgada y comestible; su pulpa es dulce y fragante."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_55c237c5","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAOTERM","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-03-25T17:04:13"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"en","value":"The fruit consists of a drupe of different size according to varieties, ovally-shaped and with yellowish orange colour in both skin and pulp. The skin is very thin and edible; the pulp, sweet and fragrant."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_94408413","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAOTERM","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-03-25T17:04:57"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"fr","value":"Le fruit est un